<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 01:11:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市下滑，美元坚挺，通胀和盈利迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-13/</link><description>亚洲股市周一下跌，而美元则守在 14 个月高位附近，此前一份明确强劲的非农就业报告推高了债券收益率，并在财报季即将到来之际测试了高企的股票估值。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 00:37:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：热门美国就业数据引发收益率火热，批评股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2025-01-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 21:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2025-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国加强制裁以遏制俄罗斯向中国和印度供应石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tougher-us-sanctions-curb-russian-oil-supply-china-india-2025-01-12/</link><description>中国和印度炼油厂将从中东、非洲和美洲采购更多石油，从而推高价格和运输成本。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 11:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tougher-us-sanctions-curb-russian-oil-supply-china-india-2025-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>央行行长潘基文在京会见英国央行总裁贝利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-central-bank-governor-pan-meets-boes-bailey-beijing-2025-01-12/</link><description>中国央行周日表示，中国人民银行行长潘功胜周六在北京会见了英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利，讨论了金融稳定与合作等话题。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 04:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-central-bank-governor-pan-meets-boes-bailey-beijing-2025-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，赞比亚证券交易委员会因不当销售中国房地产债券而对渣打银行实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/zambias-sec-sanctions-standard-chartered-over-china-property-bond-mis-selling-2025-01-11/</link><description>据消息人士透露，赞比亚证券交易委员会 (SEC) 已对渣打银行实施制裁，原因是渣打银行在赞比亚房地产危机最严重的时期向该银行的一名当地财富客户不当出售一家中国房地产公司的债券。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 15:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/zambias-sec-sanctions-standard-chartered-over-china-property-bond-mis-selling-2025-01-11/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国黑客威胁的加剧，拜登将下令实施更严格的网络安全标准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/china-hacking-threat-builds-biden-order-tougher-cybersecurity-standards-2025-01-10/</link><description>根据该命令的草案，总统乔·拜登呼吁在未来几天发布的新行政命令中对联邦机构和承包商实施更严格的网络安全标准，推动旨在解决与中国相关的重复网络操作和网络犯罪活动的改革路透社看到。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 21:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/china-hacking-threat-builds-biden-order-tougher-cybersecurity-standards-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国今年有充足的财政空间促进经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-has-ample-fiscal-space-bolster-growth-this-year-2025-01-10/</link><description>财政部副部长廖敏周五表示，中国今年有充足的财政政策空间和工具来支持经济增长，并将加大支出刺激投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-has-ample-fiscal-space-bolster-growth-this-year-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级立法者向伦敦证券交易所和监管机构表达了对 Shein 的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/senior-uk-lawmaker-flags-concerns-about-shein-lse-regulator-2025-01-10/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席周四写信给伦敦证券交易所，对 Shein 代表在本周的听证会上提供的证据表示担忧，并询问交易所如何检查寻求上市的公司的声明。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/senior-uk-lawmaker-flags-concerns-about-shein-lse-regulator-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>沙利文表示，美国已对与中国有关的电信公司网络攻击做出回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-has-responded-chinese-linked-cyber-attacks-telecoms-firms-sullivan-says-2025-01-10/</link><description>美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文周五表示，美国已采取措施应对与中国有关的针对美国电信公司的网络间谍活动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-has-responded-chinese-linked-cyber-attacks-telecoms-firms-sullivan-says-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>缅甸接连发生电信诈骗事件后，中国警告公民谨防电信诈骗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-citizens-telecom-fraud-after-reports-scams-myanmar-2025-01-10/</link><description>中国驻缅甸大使馆周五敦促中国公民警惕电信和网络诈骗，此前多起报道称，公民被宣传“高薪海外工作”的网络诈骗引诱到缅甸边境城镇苗瓦迪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 13:59:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-citizens-telecom-fraud-after-reports-scams-myanmar-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员要求政府考虑限制向中国军方出口生物技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-ask-government-consider-curbs-biotech-exports-chinas-military-2025-01-10/</link><description>一个由两党议员组成的小组呼吁拜登政府考虑限制向中国军方出口美国生物技术，理由是担心北京可能将其武器化以制造更多有毒病原体。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-ask-government-consider-curbs-biotech-exports-chinas-military-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>据美国有线电视新闻网报道，中国黑客入侵了美国外国投资审查机构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-breached-us-govt-office-that-assesses-foreign-investments-2025-01-10/</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 周五援引三名知情美国官员的话报道，中国黑客入侵了美国外国投资委员会 (CFIUS)，该委员会是一个审查外国投资是否存在国家安全风险的政府机构。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-breached-us-govt-office-that-assesses-foreign-investments-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>最高法院似乎倾向于维持 TikTok 在美国的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/supreme-court-hear-fight-over-looming-us-ban-tiktok-2025-01-10/</link><description>周五，最高法院似乎倾向于维持一项法律，该法律将在 1 月 19 日之前强制在美国出售或禁止流行的短视频应用程序 TikTok，法官们重点关注的是对中国的国家安全担忧，从而引发了此次镇压。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:08:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/supreme-court-hear-fight-over-looming-us-ban-tiktok-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>西藏地震突显世界屋脊大坝的地震风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibet-quake-highlights-earthquake-risk-dams-roof-world-2025-01-10/</link><description>专家表示，西藏本周发生的 6.8 级地震造成 126 人死亡，四座水库受损，凸显了亚洲大国中国和印度在世界上最偏远、地震多发地区之一疯狂建设水电的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:41:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibet-quake-highlights-earthquake-risk-dams-roof-world-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>视频显示中国西北地区民众与警察发生冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/people-clash-with-police-northwest-china-videos-show-2025-01-10/</link><description>据社交媒体上的视频显示，中国西北部的陕西省一所职业学校外发生了罕见的抗议活动，一群人与警察发生冲突，本月早些时候，一名学生死亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/people-clash-with-police-northwest-china-videos-show-2025-01-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>